<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ạ̹ʿjny wsẖklny bạ̹dyk wʿlmny ạ̹tkl ʿlyk
 hạlʿạlm mn ḥwly qạsy ʿm ysqyny ạlmr bkạsy
 mạfyy ʿysẖ ạlqdạsẗ wạlʿạlm mn ḥwly hyk
 ʿṭyny mn rwḥk qdsny wʿlmny ạ̹tkl ʿlyk
 1- bjrb ạ̹ny gẖyr ḥạly ʿysẖ mlyḥ wblạ mạ ạ̹gẖlṭ
 ṣạr ly mdẗ ʿly̱ hạlḥạlẗ wlạ mrẗ bḥạwl wbtẓbṭ
 myn qạdr ysẖfʿ fy ykẖlṣny mn ạlkẖṭyẗ
 ạ̉nạ mn qlby bdy ṭyʿk wạlṭạʿẗ ṣʿbẗ ʿly
 2- ạ̉nạ knt bhạlʿạlm ḍạyʿ kạnt ạ̉ʿmạly tjrsny
 knt bqyt bsẖry wạqʿ lwmạ bạlnʿmẗ tkẖlṣny
 ạ̉nạ kẖạyf ḍyʿ mn jdyd wạ̹rjʿ ʿnk ṣyr bʿyd
 ạ̉ḥmyny ạ̉nt ạmskny bạ̹ydk ạ̉nạ kẖwfy sẖy msẖ bạlạ̹yd</lyrics>
<title>ạ̹ʿjny wsẖklny bạ̹dyk</title>
